```plantuml
@startuml Bytom-Community_Bytom-Server

actor User
participant "gRPC API" as GRPC
participant "TxPool" as TxPool
participant "Blockchain Core" as BC
participant "Mining" as Mining
participant "Peer-to-Peer Networking" as P2P
participant "Block Synchronization" as NetSync
participant "Database" as DB

User -> GRPC: Send transaction request
GRPC -> TxPool: Validate and add transaction
TxPool -> BC: Check for double-spending
BC -> TxPool: Confirm transaction validity
TxPool -> GRPC: Transaction added successfully

User -> GRPC: Request block synchronization
GRPC -> NetSync: Initiate block synchronization
NetSync -> P2P: Discover peers and request blocks
P2P -> NetSync: Receive blocks from peers
NetSync -> BC: Validate and add blocks
BC -> DB: Store updated blockchain state
DB -> BC: Acknowledge data storage

User -> GRPC: Start mining operation
GRPC -> Mining: Begin mining process
Mining -> BC: Create block template
Mining -> BC: Submit mined block
BC -> DB: Store new block
DB -> BC: Acknowledge block storage
Mining -> GRPC: Mining operation completed

User -> GRPC: Access transaction data
GRPC -> DB: Query transaction by ID
DB -> GRPC: Return transaction data
GRPC -> User: Display transaction data

User -> GRPC: Request secure connection
GRPC -> P2P: Establish encrypted peer connection
P2P -> GRPC: Secure connection established

@enduml
```